    "Plain text paragraphs embedded inside the p, span, or similar tags of the HTML and XML documents were extracted using the LXML Python package.",
    "Both the abstracts and the full texts available in the body of the documents were collected in the process.",
    "Subscripts and superscripts in the text were encoded by the underscore and the caret symbols, respectively.",
    "No additional pre-processing was performed since the LLMs are generally able to 'understand' chemical entities, units, and literature references.",
